```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Domain User
  participant Client as Client PC (CL1)
  participant DC as Domain Controller (DC1)
  participant DNS as DNS Service

  User->>Client: Enter domain credentials
  Client->>DNS: Resolve DC1.saimoon.local
  DNS-->>Client: Returns DC1 IP
  Client->>DC: Authenticate (Kerberos/NTLM)
  DC-->>Client: Auth success + policy list
  Client->>DC: Download GPOs (SYSVOL)
  DC-->>Client: GPO files delivered
  Client-->>User: Desktop loads with policies applied
```